# TASK
Extract and normalize the following event details:

1. An explicit event ID if available 
1. A central datetime reference using either RFC3339 `dateTime` or all-day `date` format
3. Timezone in valid IANA format (if `dateTime` is used)
2. An IANA timezone for interpreting any time expressions  
